snippet.title: v4.1 [As Thunders Filled the Sky] Trailer - Herrscher of Thunder Descends -Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Herrscher of Thunder Descends

HI3's v4.1 [As Thunders Filled the Sky] coming soon, Raiden Mei's S-rank battlesuit [Herrscher of Thunder] debuts to cleanse all sins with thunder!
Chill out in the upcoming summer event [Gemina Invasions - Deep Paradise Arc] and you will be swimming in summer bonuses!



Subscribe our YouTube and turn on notification for latest video : http://bit.ly/HonkaiImpact3rdYTB
